    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> marinated chicken</strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray</p><p>Put the tray under the grill for 10-12 min or until the chicken is beginning to brown and is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>chicken tikka</strong></p>",
