    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel lengths off your <strong>cucumber</strong> until you end up with a pile of cucumber ribbons</p><p>Chop the <strong>remaining cucumber core</strong> finely</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped cucumber core</strong> with the <strong>remaining natural yoghurt</strong> and your<strong> mint sauce</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>cucumber & mint raita</strong></p>",
