    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong>, cut side down, and toast for 2-3 min or until beginning to brown</p>",
